                              በመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ዘሠረቃ፡ ወዘፈሐቃ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ይኩን፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">This is a book which Walatta
                              Gabrǝʾel has donated to the [<cb/>]
                              church of Māryām (in) Fäqada so that it may be for her a guide in the
                              Kingdom of Heaven. He who steals it or erases (its text) shall be
                              excommunicated by the authority of Peter and Paul.</q>
                           <note> The letter ቃ in ወዘፈሐቃ፡ is written with a horizontal upper stroke
                              characteristic of the letter for the spirantized ejective velar in
                              Tǝgrǝñña. </note>
                        </item>
